# Ecosystem Connection Framework™ (T-014)

**Full document:** `docs/ECOSYSTEM_CONNECTION_FRAMEWORK.md`

Spark is **one living ecosystem** — not separate modules. Value = relationships between experiences.

## Connection Principle™

Every experience answers: **What should naturally happen next?** Never dead ends.

## Living cycle

Question → Guidance → Momentum Builder → Spark Card → Business Asset → Gallery → Reflection → Capability Growth → smarter Guidance

## No dead ends

**One** thoughtfully chosen next recommendation. Never five competing actions. Max 3 choices (T-003).

## Gentle guidance

Recommend — never interrupt. Thoughtful bridges, not promotional. Shari test.

## Required spec fields

Leads from · strengthens · natural next (one primary) · Business Asset link when relevant · capability · EF reduction.

**Type:** `SparkEcosystemConnectionSpec` in `lib/sparkEcosystemConnection/types.ts`

## EF

Reduce decision fatigue, searching, remembering, context switching.

## Personalization (quiet)

Brain · Business Assets · journey stage · Capability Graph · Transformation Graph · priorities · recent conversation.

